        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The “Pradhan Mantri Matsya Sampada Yojana” is a centrally sponsored scheme implemented by the Department of Fisheries, Government of Uttarakhand. The scheme aims to promote the growth of the fisheries sector by providing financial assistance and technical support for modern fisheries activities, thereby increasing fish production, improving livelihood opportunities, and encouraging the adoption of advanced fisheries infrastructure among eligible beneficiaries.\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "A 60% subsidy is provided to SC/ST and Women beneficiaries for pond construction, trout units, rearing units, RAS, biofloc units, cage culture, cold storage, motorcycles with ice boxes, fish kiosks, ornamental fisheries, feed mills, hatcheries, and similar activities. A 40% subsidy is provided for all other categories, and a 20% subsidy is provided specifically for large RAS units.\n**Table-1:**\n**Activity/Item****Unit Cost per Hectare****Grant (General Category)****Grant (Women/SC/ST)****Maximum Limit/Grant Limit**Construction and investment of new ponds₹11 lakh (per hectare)₹4,40,000/-₹6,60,000/-Maximum 2 hectares individual &amp;amp;amp;amp; 20 hectares society/group etc. Trout Raceways and Investment (Nos.) 50 sq.m. per unit₹5,50,000/-₹2,20,000/-₹3,30,000/-Maximum 4 units individual &amp;amp;amp;amp; 20 units society/group etc.Large RAS (8 tanks)/Large Biofloc Unit (50 tanks)₹50,00,000/-₹10,00,000/-₹12,50,000/-Maximum 1 UnitMedium RAS (6 tanks)/Medium Biofloc Unit (25 tanks)₹25,00,000/-₹10,00,000/-₹15,00,000/-Maximum 1 UnitSmall RAS (1 tank) / Small Biofloc Unit (7 tanks)₹7,50,000/-₹3,00,000/-₹4,50,000/-Maximum 1 UnitEstablishment of Trout Fish Hatcheries ₹50,00,000/-₹20,00,000/-₹30,00,000/-Maximum 1 UnitCold Water RAS Unit₹20,00,000/-₹8,00,000/-₹12,00,000/-Maximum 1 UnitFish Kiosk₹10,00,000/-₹4,00,000/-₹6,00,000/-Maximum 1 Unit**Table-2:**\n**Activity/Item****Unit Cost****Grant (General Category)****Grant (Women/SC/ST)****Maximum Limit/Grant Limit**Motor cycle with Ice Box₹75,000/-₹30,000/-₹45,000/-Maximum 1 UnitThree wheeler with Ice Box₹3,00,000/-₹1,20,000/-₹1,80,000/-Maximum 1 UnitRefrigerated/Insulated Vehicles₹25,00,000/-₹10,00,000/-₹15,00,000/-Maximum 1 UnitCold Storage Capacity 10 Tons₹40,00,000/-₹16,00,000/-₹24,00,000/-Maximum 1 UnitEstablishment of Cage₹3,000/- per cubic meter₹1,200/-₹1,800/-Maximum 1800 cubic meters for individual &amp;amp;amp;amp; 7200 cubic meters for society/group etc. Backyard Ornamental Unit₹3,00,000/-₹1,20,000/-₹1,80,000/-Maximum 4 units for individual and 20 units for society/group etc.Feed Mill Capacity 2 Tons Per Day Production₹30,00,000/-₹12,00,000/-₹18,00,000/-  Maximum 1 Unit\n<br>\n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The scheme aims to promote growth of fisheries sector by providing financial assistance & technical support for modern fisheries activities, thereby increasing fish production,improving livelihood opportunities,& encouraging adoption of advanced fisheries infrastructure among eligible beneficiaries.",
        "detailedDescription": [
          {
            "type": "align_justify",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The “Pradhan Mantri Matsya Sampada Yojana” is a centrally sponsored scheme implemented by the Department of Fisheries, Government of Uttarakhand. The scheme aims to promote the growth of the fisheries sector by providing financial assistance and technical support for modern fisheries activities, thereby increasing fish production, improving livelihood opportunities, and encouraging the adoption of advanced fisheries infrastructure among eligible beneficiaries."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
